item.title: [Source][VB] OpenURL
item.dc:creator: @Freddy1990 Freddy1990
item.description:
@Freddy1990 wrote:

Well, this is some code to open an url, like you'd use an inet, only this creates this inet itself:

Function OpenURL(URL As String) As String
Dim tmpInet As Object
        Set tmpInet = CreateObject("InetCtls.Inet")
        OpenURL = tmpInet.OpenURL(URL)
        tmpInet.Cancel
End Function
